Field.Label:
This plugin provides Model Context Protocol (MCP) support, allowing AI assistants like Claude to interact with your Indigo installation.

The MCP server runs automatically when the plugin starts and provides:
• Natural language search for devices, variables, and actions
• Read-only access to all Indigo entities
• Semantic search powered by OpenAI embeddings

To use with Claude Desktop, add this to your claude_desktop_config.json:
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "indigo": {
      "command": "indigo-plugin-host",
      "args": ["com.vtmikel.mcp_server"]
    }
  }
}
